             was indicted for <rs id="t17980704-7-off26" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980704-7-off26" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980704-7-off26" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17980704-7-cd27" type="crimeDate">9th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980704-7-off26 t17980704-7-cd27"></join>, a silver table spoon, value 15s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17980704-7-victim91" type="victimName">
                     David 
                     Morley
                  <interp inst="t17980704-7-victim91" type="surname" value="Morley"></interp>
